---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<Layout title="About APA Maritime" description="Learn about APA Maritime's 25+ years of experience in maritime logistics and shipping solutions.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <Image
        src="/images/about.jpeg"
        alt="About APA Maritime"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        width={1920}
        height={1080}
        loading="eager"
      />
      <!-- Dark overlay for better text readability -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary opacity-60"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="container-custom relative z-10 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-slide-up">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">About APA Maritime</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-100">
          With over 25 years of industry expertise, we've established ourselves as a trusted leader in maritime logistics and shipping solutions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
        <div class="animate-slide-right">
          <h2 class="section-title">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            APA Maritime stands as a premier maritime solutions provider, committed to delivering comprehensive and integrated services across the global shipping value chain. The company’s mission is centred on empowering clients with strategic advantages, enhancing operational efficiency, and driving sustainable growth within a dynamic and complex industry.

This vision is realised through three core pillars:

Expert chartering and commercial operations of oil, chemical, and gas tankers

Specialised shipbroking services tailored to diverse client needs

A robust portfolio of maritime consulting offerings that provide strategic insights and solutions

In an era defined by market volatility, increasingly stringent environmental regulations, and rapid technological advancements, APA Maritime distinguishes itself through profound domain expertise, an integrated service approach, and proactive market foresight.

The company's unique value proposition extends far beyond facilitating transactions. APA Maritime delivers end-to-end strategic guidance that helps clients mitigate risks, optimise performance, and adopt future-ready solutions—particularly within the evolving LNG, LPG, oil, and chemical tanker sectors.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-slide-left">
          <div class="bg-linear-to-br from-primary to-primary-light rounded-lg p-12 text-white">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Our Values</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-lg">Reliability & Trust</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-lg">Innovation & Excellence</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-lg">Customer Focus</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-lg">Global Expertise</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats Section -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 py-12 border-t border-b border-gray-200">
        <div class="text-center animate-scale-in">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">25+</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Years in Business</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center animate-scale-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">500+</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Successful Shipments</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center animate-scale-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">50+</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Global Partners</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center animate-scale-in" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">100%</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Client Satisfaction</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <h2 class="section-title mb-6">Ready to Partner With Us?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Let's discuss how APA Maritime can help with your shipping and logistics needs.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

